後入左degree social science<br />\n但而家目標無變到<br />\n諗住搏高GAP同做多D義工<br />\n第時再駁上社工MASTER"},{"pid":"93defbf1a5fedfd46b88282fea569998863cc71b","tid":350134,"uid":113429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"885cc3191fa7f68f87d9e200904fa2bc19e79500","tid":350134,"uid":12579,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"當年想入ust science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想研究海洋生物<br />\n誤打誤撞做左兩年asshole仔  果陣成個人咩方向都冇<br />\n又衰貪玩上唔翻岸<br />\n好彩之後護士學校收左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndse同gpa都爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b3fbfed5b9ee7ca4c5129c127c2a2ab1c41e62","tid":350134,"uid":135068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想做社工<br />\nREPEAT左一年但都係唔夠分<br />\nJUPAS,樹仁都唔收<br />\n最後入左degree social science<br />\n但而家目標無變到<br />\n諗住搏高GAP同做多D義工<br />\n第時再駁上社工MASTER</blockquote><br />\n街外人讀果個master 社工<br />\n同 degree 社工 升果個master社工唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩分別 巴打可唔可以講講"},{"pid":"b890891b1edf31364b75325b35601e5de4900e48","tid":350134,"uid":134423,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T14:01:30.000Z","msg":"小學覺得電腦勁嘅人好型，所以想做電腦工程師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大個先知佢地係IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a854da51599bf434b1d7436c98e5e938b78bcb9","tid":350134,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65c57ca5afb64193eaa42ed8a563f32ff7664de7","tid":350134,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想做社工<br />\nREPEAT左一年但都係唔夠分<br />\nJUPAS,樹仁都唔收<br />\n最後入左degree social science<br />\n但而家目標無變到<br />\n諗住搏高GAP同做多D義工<br />\n第時再駁上社工MASTER</blockquote><br />\n街外人讀果個master 社工<br />\n同 degree 社工 升果個master社工唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩分別 巴打可唔可以講講</blockquote><br />\n街外人MASTER 讀完 NGO都係當你 HD<br />\n做唔到SWO<br />\n最多做SWA 衰啲 WW 都有<br />\n <br />\n始終4年 degree 加實習時數<br />\n你一個master由頭讀起係做唔到同人一樣<br />\n唔係打擊巴打你 但事實的確係咁<br />\n加上社工飽和 你連degree都無入行最多做下把位</blockquote><br />\n無知一問 讀個有社工牌既master都唔ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c69c2ef51edb74683bd3c8e7a2b841d352c8de7","tid":350134,"uid":135068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想做社工<br />\nREPEAT左一年但都係唔夠分<br />\nJUPAS,樹仁都唔收<br />\n最後入左degree social science<br />\n但而家目標無變到<br />\n諗住搏高GAP同做多D義工<br />\n第時再駁上社工MASTER</blockquote><br />\n街外人讀果個master 社工<br />\n同 degree 社工 升果個master社工唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩分別 巴打可唔可以講講</blockquote><br />\n街外人MASTER 讀完 NGO都係當你 HD<br />\n做唔到SWO<br />\n最多做SWA 衰啲 WW 都有<br />\n <br />\n始終4年 degree 加實習時數<br />\n你一個master由頭讀起係做唔到同人一樣<br />\n唔係打擊巴打你 但事實的確係咁<br />\n加上社工飽和 你連degree都無入行最多做下把位</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就更清楚自己要更努力 <br />\n起碼都要更多參加社會服務<br />\n當然下年eapp 樹仁收左我就會trans過去啦<br />\n不過我想問下如果poly， cuscs收左<br />\n由hd駁上去好定msw會比較好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070c304da87dcf04ca41d532809b06dc17ebb7ac","tid":350134,"uid":87196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"前：自由自在嘅作家<br />\n後：收入良好嘅it 佬"},{"pid":"0f900c201f80589c8509ab568b45f5115ce36d0a","